formThreeBId.notesToCertificate: N. Aangan Project consist total six towers A,B,C,D,E,F which is approved under RERA.  However, considering current market situation and response in the area, the promoters have decided to drop three towers namely D, E and F. As per Affidavit Cum Declaration dated 23.10.2020.  Tower A, B and C are fully completed with total cost of Rs. 8,59,24,333 (Land Cost Rs. 46,82,527 and Development Cost Rs. 8,12,41,806). As informed to us, promoters have provided all the facilities as per approved plan to customer of Tower A, B and C and they have also applied for project completion certificate with local authority which is under process. Based on this facts, the promoters need not to retain any fund in the Designated Account and they are eligible to withdraw full amount receivable from the customers in future also towards booking of remaining flats in Tower A,B and C.
